op\" module_class=\"about-page-content\" _builder_version=\"3.9\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|desktop\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"3.0.47\" padding_tablet=\"30px|0px|0px|0px\" padding_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" padding_bottom=\"30px\" padding_left=\"50px\" padding_right=\"50px\" padding_top=\"75px\" background_color=\"#ffffff\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\" background_repeat=\"no-repeat\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text h1 header\" _builder_version=\"3.0.89\" header_font=\"|700|||||||\" header_font_size=\"35px\" header_font_size_tablet=\"33px\" header_font_size_phone=\"27px\" header_font_size_last_edited=\"on|phone\" custom_margin=\"||20px|\"]<h1>Our Mission</h1>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"3.9\"]<p>At <strong>guinea</strong>pig, we want to help people to understand and improve their health and fitness.We are pursuing the third SDG (Sustainable Development Goal) from the <a href=\"https://www.un.org/sustainabledevelopment/health/\">United Nations</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>\"Ensure healthy lives and promote well-being for all at all ages.\"</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>If you want to join us on this mission, you can do so in three simple ways:</p>\n<p>1. Work to understand and improve your own health and fitness, as well as the health and fitness of your friends, family, and community. We are hard at work to help you do this with<strong>guinea</strong>pig.</p>\n<p>2. Partner with <strong>guinea</strong>pig to offer your health and fitness products and services on our marketplace.</p>\n<p>3. Come and work with us at <strong>guinea</strong>pig! We need all the help we can get to pursue this moonshot mission.</p>\n<p>We can\'t wait to hear which path you choose.</p>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text - signature\" _builder_version=\"3.0.89\" text_font=\"Reenie Beanie||||||||\" text_text_color=\"#232323\" text_font_size=\"45px\" text_line_height=\"1.1\" text_orientation=\"right\" module_alignment=\"right\" custom_margin=\"